Installation Instructions
*************************


    Hermit requires CMake (version  2.4 or later). You can obtain CMake sources here http://cmake.org/.


Run CMake generator:

    cmake .

Then configure hermit:

    ccmake .

Then make:

    make

And finally install:

    make install

Package makers can specify DESTDIR:
    
    make install DESTDIR="destdir"

To remove hermit:

    make uninstall

